{"tid":408834,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(有GIF有透) 睇左Watchmen終極剪輯版,廢老勿入","createTime":"2017-09-21T14:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T13:08:33.000Z","uid":49391,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a84a46840744b03a108d73c3f1f1f649c7f5dad","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:10:56.000Z","msg":"magnet:?xt=urn:btih:dbfae89938a3476bc2cbc2fea2382562bc4a1035<br />\n<br />\n好多年前睇過非剪輯版,見佢出左終極剪輯版,所以搵黎重睇<br />\n本身好少會搵戲黎重睇,覺得世上有咁多經典好戲未睇,點解仲要花時間去睇D睇過嘅戲呢? 有時間不如睇D未睇過架啦<br />\n但出左加長版就唔同講法#lol# <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KKS0I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKKS0I.gif&h=239ff12c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n守望者前身，民兵組織，左起分別是：側影、飛蛾俠、美鈔人、夜梟一代、都會隊長、笑匠、絲靈一代、正義面罩。<br />\n笑匠是唯一一個後來的守望者成員，笑匠加入民兵時是最年輕的的一個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KiVXU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKiVXU.gif&h=d7e90ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勝利之吻,歷史上真有其人其事#lol# <br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%83%9C%E5%88%A9%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2583%259C%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2590%25BB&d=aABYJEMAYwL%2BH9AytDrICNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0460c054\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%83%9C%E5%88%A9%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%BB</a>"},{"pid":"aecfacf2b27d9bd36733f56aefb3480062a1dc35","tid":408834,"uid":18818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:17:58.000Z","msg":"DLC咁撚無恥你都睇#lol#"},{"pid":"af99c553de63ee3ee83ed4419cf8e69073ce3ff7","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KKFMa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKKFMa.gif&h=c967e6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原型係法國攝影師Marc Riboud的作品:<br />\nThe Ultimate Confrontation: The Flower and the Bayonet <br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Ultimate_Confrontation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FThe_Ultimate_Confrontation&d=aABYJEMAYwL%2BH9AytDrICNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3f2228b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Ultimate_Confrontation</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KKatj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKKatj.gif&h=bb1e9497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n守望者，左起分別是：笑匠、絲靈二代（一代的女兒）、曼哈頓博士、法老王（奧茲曼迪斯）、夜梟二代（丹）、羅夏"},{"pid":"fd28a276cac0465e94d67e238206e3af292899b1","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KKrRA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKKrRA.gif&h=22702b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KK6QN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKK6QN.gif&h=558ca2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n著到咁,難怪羅夏叫佢做whores<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(其實之後仲同笑匠、夜梟一代有染)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KKDsM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKKDsM.gif&h=85b85a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b429c0fd4fef198e61fe4fdd10888a337b52144c","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KKKK3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKKKK3.gif&h=5880e060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ndr.manhattan打越戰,完全係單方面虐殺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後美國贏左越戰,越南仲成為美國第51區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n漫畫版:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KK9ug.jpg\" 