391,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩放監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦ON9仔,點解睇親舊戲都有呢D柒頭撲出黎<br />\n咪撚睇舊戲舊劇舊AV啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"a0264364ba03ea095003defd0dd93fe28c329083","tid":408834,"uid":41402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7be50c6c7099b9cbd3bcfc441ed664fce7476f62","tid":408834,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"n 年前睇過<br />\n套戲有咩意思？"},{"pid":"79d5877902448d627fae9d98dcb5e9ebe118e9ba","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Kz2Hp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKz2Hp.gif&h=25a72325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一打二都游刃有餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOzymandias算唔算&quot;超人&quot;有D爭議<br />\n但佢將自己體能同心智都練到極限<br />\n肯定係人類的頂峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1a49498f7ef73fb2dd03e60bc446fcf75ad015","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>n 年前睇過<br />\n套戲有咩意思？</blockquote><br />\n對超級英雄的解构及批判<br />\n<br />\n引起結果正義及程序正義的反思"},{"pid":"6cc7e293ce01bf391ac384d00466632e3c06edcb","tid":408834,"uid":125223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"拎過雨果獎"},{"pid":"414126a81f1394235e67d1ceb7bbfa9847b47eb8","tid":408834,"uid":125223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎過雨果獎</blockquote><br />\n唯一一套漫畫"},{"pid":"b36856a9c26075f2f51866f151e39b61985abb2b","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KzEYz.md.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKzEYz.md.gif&h=1ae1c487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n漫畫好似係Ozymandias整左大怪物去破壞城市,同電影整炸彈有D出入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KzHyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKzHyb.jpg&h=aaca55fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報紙檔老闆同睇漫畫的細路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KztgP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKztgP.jpg&h=7beffaae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後同所有響漫畫出現過的普通人一樣,被作者派便當<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KzJ96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKzJ96.jpg&h=a1c17bfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n災後,呢幕電影無<br />\n剛在搭正12點,同末日鐘的意思一樣,代表末日到來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0359beaa65ab93696d45b59ce78ca4bca08b029","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KzNeu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKzNeu.gif&h=f28c2da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人類的頂點Ozymandias面對Doctor Manhattan只可以慌忙逃竄,霸氣盡失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDoctor Manhattan之後仲要串佢:&quot;The worlds smartest man poses no more a threat to me then the worlds smartest termite&quot;. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f2798ea3c5cd36f9316f4382a0631c7c60b20e","tid":408834,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:53:05.000Z","msg":"結局係世界末日左？"},{"pid":"622c8881c7ec02e67b339704f306c4df978362f5","tid":408834,"uid":15116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:06:15.000Z","msg":"當年上影個陣英雄電影未興起 <br />\n加上題材更加係少有既反英雄<br />\n所以票房慘淡<br />\n只能說導演走得太前<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb7ab84e459a0020eb0f8641a29a8c625603078","tid":408834,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結局係世界末日左？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 當蘇聯同美國既共同敵人消失左<br />\n世界就和平翻"},{"pid":"b2f0e0dc55ae0a03e6bc58dfddaefae53eb5f183","tid":408834,"uid":7034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拎過雨果獎</blockquote><br />\n唯一一套漫畫</blockquote><br />\n而家雨果獎好似有一個係專俾圖像啲 但watchmen拎果時係冇"},{"pid":"d7a6174df98043163ba54dc7198749682005472b","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"羅夏:永不妥協,即使面對世界末日.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KzaWU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKzaWU.gif&h=b56bfffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為凡人,我地日日都要妥協,有時為份工向仆街上司妥協、為某單交易向仆街客戶妥協、為某段感情向發脾氣的男女朋友妥協......<br />\n妥協唔係為帶來咩重大利益、得到D咩野,好多時只係為左唔想失去更多,響社會生存,就要學識妥協<br />\n所以一個人話佢永不妥協,佢必然成為一個殉道者,等緊佢嘅結局就係一條末路──死亡,作者已經明示左了<br />\n<br />\n正因為如此,羅夏係我最喜歡的角色,世上太多識得妥協的人了;唔識妥協,非黑即白,為自己的信仰直面死亡,如羅夏一樣的人太希罕了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KzS8m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKzS8m.jpg&h=654d2a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KzrUq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKzrUq.jpg&h=43ea0075&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d887bbc53e6ff0cdfa477492c73d11192d48bced","tid":408834,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:15:11.000Z","msg":"果陣入戲院睇, 覺得好正<br />\n<br />\n但呢個post入面咁多場景都好似未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺我要重睇"},{"pid":"bbbd949791e65a42ed7e38f83298e50fd32152ef","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年上影個陣英雄電影未興起 <br />\n加上題材更加係少有既反英雄<br />\n所以票房慘淡<br />\n只能說導演走得太前<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔前,唔前<br />\n試下思考以下問題<br />\n一套戲何謂成功?票房?藝術性?一套高藝術性低票房的經典電影能稱得上失敗嗎?<br />\n<br />\n試下咁諗,如果響流行反英雄電影的時代,導演先去拍呢套,唔係有點隨波逐流了嗎?<br />\n正因為導演走得前,佢先可以響反英雄電影題材上面,成為一個先驅者、開拓者的角色;而且響呢個題材上面,WATCHMEN呢套戲會係好多年都無戲可以超越到的經典"},{"pid":"3f848343f7e71b404f00e1b0c9c4353a46b9da34","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果陣入戲院睇, 覺得好正<br />\n<br />\n但呢個post入面咁多場景都好似未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺我要重睇</blockquote><br />\n上映版156分鐘，剪輯版182分鐘，終極剪輯版215分鐘<br />\n<br />\n有D戲唔同年紀睇有唔同感受,如果你時隔多年再睇呢套,可能畀到你另一番感受同體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb580cce7cf1e4869f5599fe1b5d7450eddb08c","tid":408834,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://movie.douban.com/review/3269225/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmovie.douban.com%2Freview%2F3269225%2F&d=aABYJEMAYwL%2BH9AytDrICNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=85582ba9\" target=\"_blank\">https://movie.douban.com/review/3269225/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度列出左終極剪輯版比上映版多左咩鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8382053459e7fc002506f5fe7e0ae402c153002e","tid":408834,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年上影個陣英雄電影未興起 <br />\n加上題材更加係少有既反英雄<br />\n所以票房慘淡<br />\n只能說導演走得太前<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家上畫一樣仆街<br />\n隨時重多負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/no